incidents.name: A subset of customers in the EMEA region may have experienced degraded performance during Zoom meetings.

incident_updates.body: This incident has been resolved.

Between 10:10 to 11:10 UTC, a subset of customers in the EMEA region may have experienced degraded performance during Zoom meetings due to an outage related to one of our cloud service provider. We continue to monitor for any changes in services.

incidents.name: An issue impacting our email services

incident_updates.body: This incident has been resolved.
We have resolved the issue impacting our email services. We will continue to monitor and provide updates as we have them.

We are investigating an issue impacting our email services which is preventing emails from being sent for meeting related information, including: meeting/webinar invites, sign up verification, recording status updates, and OTP login.

incidents.name: Issue with Zoom Phone services and Zoom Meetings

incident_updates.body: Between 18:56 -19:20 UTC a subset of customers in the US may have experienced impact to Zoom Phone services and Zoom Meetings presenting as degraded video/audio quality, call interruption, or call failure due to a regional level fiber event from one of our carriers.  While the event is over, we continue to monitor for any changes or issues.
